metadata.name: Moment of collision
metadata.description: #2Moment of collision A little confused, because I do not know what is going to happen, all the busy memories of my mind are repeated, images of people I loved, best friends and family, I remember, beautiful days that passed, and in the back of my mind I was, and for a long time I did not remember them, and more than any moment I regretted being in that moment, a little later I saw a yellow light in front of my eyes, a bright light, I went back to the present, I am in the middle of a street, waiting Collision, collision and the end of this cycle ...
